      <title>遭受台风袭击的东南亚准备迎接更多暴雨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/typhoon-ravaged-southeast-asia-braces-for-more-heavy-rain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计本周末东南亚将出现更多降雨，降雨量将进一步增加，超强台风八木造成的损失将进一步加剧。八木是今年袭击亚洲的最强台风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/typhoon-ravaged-southeast-asia-braces-for-more-heavy-rain</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 07:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
