      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 05:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯攻击或迫使乌克兰钢铁制造商进口煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/russian-assault-may-force-ukrainian-steelmakers-to-import-coal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果俄罗斯军队攻占顿涅茨克地区前线附近的乌克兰唯一一座煤矿，乌克兰钢铁制造商可能被迫进口炼焦煤，给陷入困境的乌克兰钢铁行业再一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/russian-assault-may-force-ukrainian-steelmakers-to-import-coal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
